author: Kelly Cohen
title: New Fiorina ad fires salvo at Hillary Clinton
text:
Republican presidential candidate Carly Fiorina takes on her Democratic rival Hillary Clinton in a new ad.
In the 140-second spot comparing scenes of the two answering questions from the Republican and Democratic presidential debates, Fiorina focuses on their differences on immigration, foreign policy, national security, Benghazi and what Fiorina calls Clinton's "track record of lying."
Watch the ad, dubbed "Carly Fiorina tops Hillary Clinton in head to head matchup."
In a Quinnipiac University poll released in late September, the former Hewlett-Packard CEO tops the former secretary of state in a head-to-head general election matchup, 44 percent to 43 percent.
